### 1. Register Organization + First Admin User
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orgName": "Helena Coaching",
  "orgSlug": "helena-coaching",
  "billingEmail": "billing@helenacoaching.com",
  "firstName": "Admin",
  "lastName": "User",
  "email": "admin@helenacoaching.com",
  "password": "ChangeMe123!"
}

### 2. Login
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@helenacoaching.com",
  "password": "ChangeMe123!"
}

### 3. Create HR Manager
POST http://localhost:3000/api/users
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer PASTE_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "firstName": "Helena",
  "lastName": "Smith",
  "email": "hr@helenacoaching.com",
  "password": "ChangeMe123!",
  "role": "hr_manager"
}

### 4. Create Manager
POST http://localhost:3000/api/users
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer PASTE_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "firstName": "James",
  "lastName": "Brown",
  "email": "manager@helenacoaching.com",
  "password": "ChangeMe123!",
  "role": "manager"
}

